	abstract = {A volcanic source of variation 
             
              The Atlantic Multidecadal Oscillation ({AMO}), a 50- to 70-year quasiperiodic variation of climate centered in the North Atlantic region, was long thought to be an internal oscillation of the climate system. Mann 
